{
  "stem": "3928.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the planes never came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And nobody ever came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The Germans was already going to Austria, to the German border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were ready to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And when suddenly see that nothing happened, they all came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they took-- went up to the king's palace, to where Admiral Horthy was, his residence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They put-- rolled him in, into a Persian carpet, so people don't see it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But first, they killed all his bodyguards, the palace guards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And took him, Austria, to a-- a camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "To a-- it wasn't a concentration camp, just what they call a safe camp, whatever they call it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You know, when-- like average people put concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They put in a comfortable place, where they can keep an eye on them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the Germans came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And next day, the Nazis took over completely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "The Arrow Cross people took over the country completely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And start to-- and it cost 300,000 Jewish lives, because that's when all them, right away, started to deport all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This-- and I find out, the following day, when I went up there to Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schweikert, and I asked him, what happened?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did this happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, it was a mistake for to begin with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Secret Service planned this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The military planned this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in the last minute, it was stopped by the so-called diplomats, because, in Yalta, Roosevelt, Stalin, and Churchill agreed this-- the Russians will occupy Hungary.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they could not break this agreement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the reason they did not send the paratroopers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was one day, October 15, 1944, which I never forget.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I was still active part, naturally, whatever I had to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
